b'[<p><i><b>UFC 54: Boiling Point</b></i> was a <a href="/wiki/Mixed_martial_arts" title="Mixed martial arts">mixed martial arts</a> event held by the <a href="/wiki/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship" title="Ultimate Fighting Championship">Ultimate Fighting Championship</a> on August 20, 2005, at the <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/MGM_Grand_Arena" title="MGM Grand Arena">MGM Grand Arena</a> in <a href="/wiki/Las_Vegas_Valley" title="Las Vegas Valley">Las Vegas</a>, <a href="/wiki/Nevada" title="Nevada">Nevada</a>. The event was broadcast live on <a href="/wiki/Pay-per-view" title="Pay-per-view">pay-per-view</a> in the <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">United States</a>, and later released on <a href="/wiki/DVD" title="DVD">DVD</a>.\n</p>, <p>Headlining the card were <a href="/wiki/Chuck_Liddell" title="Chuck Liddell">Chuck Liddell</a>, the Light Heavyweight champion, and <a href="/wiki/Jeremy_Horn" title="Jeremy Horn">Jeremy Horn</a>.\n</p>]'